query:
/*+  */ select acc.location,
count(*)
from question AS q1
inner join tag_question AS tq1
on q1.id = tq1.question_id AND q1.favorite_count >= 1 AND q1.favorite_count <= 10
inner join tag AS t1
on t1.id = tq1.tag_id AND t1.name IN ('idioms',
'jquery',
'object-oriented',
'prepositions',
'terminology')
inner join answer AS a1
on q1.id = a1.question_id
inner join so_user AS u1
on a1.owner_user_id = u1.id AND u1.reputation >= 10 AND u1.reputation <= 100000
inner join site AS s
on s.site_id = a1.site_id AND s.site_id = t1.site_id AND s.site_id = tq1.site_id AND s.site_id = u1.site_id AND s.site_id = q1.site_id AND s.site_name IN ('codereview',
'english',
'gis',
'salesforce')
inner join badge AS b
on s.site_id = b.site_id AND b.user_id = u1.id AND b.name IN ('Civic Duty',
'Cleanup',
'Explainer',
'Fanatic',
'Good Question',
'Guru',
'Mortarboard',
'Promoter',
'Reviewer',
'Suffrage',
'Tag Editor',
'Taxonomist')
inner join account AS acc
on acc.id = u1.account_id group by acc.location order by count(*) desc LIMIT 100;
